DPAPI is a Windows API that provides data protection services to secure sensitive data. such as private keys. passwords. and other secrets. By obtaining the DPAPI backup keys. an attacker can potentially decrypt sensitive data stored on the target system or impersonate users. gaining unauthorized access to other systems and resources.
